job.title: EMRS Principal, PGT & TGT Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 3479 Vacancy
job.body:
Total Vacancies:3479

Name of the post:

  • Principal, Vice Principal, PGT, TGT 

Description:

The Ministry of Tribal Affairs, Eklavya Model Residential Schools (EMRS) issued a total of 3479 vacancies for the posts of Principal, Vice Principal, PGT, TGT. The online application for these posts under EMRSshall starts from 01-04-2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 30-04-2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for EMRS Principal, PGT & TGT Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • Available Soon

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 01-04-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 31-05-2021

Educational qualification:

  • Educational qualification will be available soon

Age limit criteria:

  • This Information will also available soon

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Principal, Vice Principal, PGT, TGT is INR 44,900/month
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that EMRS issued this notification for which posts.

 

How to apply for EMRS Principal, PGT & TGT Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of EMRS.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Principal, Vice Principal, PGT, TGT.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
